<font color="yellow">It was a simple joke!
A white...</font>

28
00:01:22,300 --> 00:01:23,700
<font color="yellow">lie.</font>

29
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:26,500
<font color="yellow">I told you to fix that nasty
