39
00:01:55,890 --> 00:01:57,390
<font color="yellow">I thought you said it was just some
nonsense you said while drinking.</font>

40
00:01:57,390 --> 00:01:59,200
<font color="yellow">A white lie.</font>

41
00:02:01,090 --> 00:02:03,390
<font color="yellow">Stop acting cutesy.</font>

42
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:09,490
