45
00:02:49,490 --> 00:02:52,890
<font color="yellow"><i>Should I come clean now?
That'd be best, right?</i></font>

46
00:02:53,890 --> 00:02:58,100
<font color="yellow"><i>I'm sorry! It was all a lie!
I deserve to die for what I've done!</i></font>

47
