49
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:07,100
<font color="yellow"><i>You believed that?</i></font>

50
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:08,990
<font color="yellow"><i>Wait, no. That approach
may be a bit dangerous.</i></font>

51
00:03:09,990 --> 00:03:12,100
<font color="yellow"><i>Should I settle for what's in between
those two options, then?</i></font>

52
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:15,700
<font color="yellow"><i>Hey, sorry. I was just messing around.</i></font>

53
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:17,700
<font color="yellow">Why are you acting like that?
