80
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,900
<font color="yellow">Well, she had high hopes, so...</font>

81
00:04:58,900 --> 00:05:06,300
<font color="yellow">No! I'm going to congratulate
you while I can! Congrats! Congrats!</font>

82
