<font color="yellow">It's okay. She's Senior Yoon, after all.</font>

88
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:30,600
<font color="yellow">I'm sure she'll rise from
the ashes soon enough.</font>

89
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:33,600
<font color="yellow">Yeah! It's Senior Yoon, after all!</font>

90
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,690
<font color="yellow">Yes! It's Senior Yoon, after all!</font>

91
00:05:49,990 --> 00:05:51,990
<font color="yellow">- What happened? Wow!
- Since when?</font>

92
00:05:51,990 --> 00:05:53,990
<font color="yellow">- I can't believe it!
- Wow!</font>

93
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:57,400
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

94
00:05:57,900 --> 00:05:59,490
<font color="yellow">Congratulations.</font>

95
00:05:59,490 --> 00:06:01,690
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Senior.</font>

96
00:06:06,690 --> 00:06:09,190
<font color="yellow">Seriously, that's amazing!</font>

97
