156
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:36,500
<font color="yellow">Continue on with what you were doing.</font>

157
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:47,590
<font color="yellow">I'm here to sell some bags.</font>

158
00:10:47,900 --> 00:10:54,090
<font color="yellow">I think you've misunderstood.
Our store doesn't buy just any bag--</font>

159
00:10:54,090 --> 00:10:56,000
<font color="yellow">So, are you going to buy it or not?</font>

160
00:10:56,900 --> 00:10:58,590
<font color="yellow">We'll buy it.</font>

161
00:10:58,590 --> 00:11:00,500
<font color="yellow">Just a moment.</font>

162
00:11:01,690 --> 00:11:03,400
<font color="yellow">Dong Joo!</font>

163
00:11:15,690 --> 00:11:17,590
<font color="yellow">Do you buy shoes, too?</font>

164
00:11:29,300 --> 00:11:31,300
<font color="yellow">Wait, not these.</font>

165
00:11:31,300 --> 00:11:33,190
<font color="yellow">I'll just be taking these back, okay?</font>

166
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:43,590
