167
00:11:43,590 --> 00:11:45,300
<font color="yellow">Are you checking the serial
numbers on the bills?</font>

168
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:47,000
<font color="yellow">Yeah, just in case.</font>

169
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,090
<font color="yellow">Want to get smacked by a wad of cash?</font>

170
00:11:49,590 --> 00:11:51,000
<font color="yellow">Are you that happy?</font>

171
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:54,000
<font color="yellow">Yeah. What do you want to eat?
I'll buy you something yummy.</font>

172
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:56,090
<font color="yellow">- It's fine.
- Why?</font>

173
00:11:57,300 --> 00:11:59,500
<font color="yellow">Do one of your girlfriends
