174
00:11:59,500 --> 00:12:00,800
<font color="yellow">Yeah.</font>

175
00:12:01,300 --> 00:12:04,690
<font color="yellow">Oh well, then. You have
to make a living, too.</font>

176
00:12:04,690 --> 00:12:07,000
<font color="yellow">Drop me off at that intersection.</font>

177
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:18,690
<font color="yellow">Call me.</font>

178
00:12:21,900 --> 00:12:23,500
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

179
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:25,690
<font color="yellow">Is it really okay for me to call you?</font>

180
00:12:25,690 --> 00:12:29,090
<font color="yellow">You crazy... what, were you
