181
00:13:02,300 --> 00:13:04,400
<font color="yellow">Are you by yourself?</font>

182
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:05,400
<font color="yellow">Yeah.</font>

183
00:13:05,900 --> 00:13:08,000
<font color="yellow">Senior Yoon.
